		(property "Description" "AMS1117-5.0 input cap. MLCC is fine HERE - the ESR requirement applies only to the AMS1117 OUTPUT cap (C38). Local bypass; C51 470uF bulk sits at power IN. 12V DC bias derates X5R 0805 to ~4-5uF effective - acceptable for input bypass. CL21A106KAYNNNE, LCSC C15850 (JLC basic)."
